# 10. 星を目指して

Tsukasa: We finally got that map back...
Nene: Yeah, but it took us the entire day.
Emu: Still, we got to do a show with those zombies, ride on a turtle and chase that phoenix around with Rion. It was a fun day in my book☆
Len: Haha. I agree!
Len: Anyway, now that we have the map again, we might be able to figure out what feelings went into this place...
Tsukasa: Right. Then, let's take another look at it.
Rui: Upon closer inspection, this map seems to cover a vast area.
Tsukasa: Yes, I'm seeing the names of several different islands...
Nene: Hey, this island has some kind of symbol next to it.
MEIKO: What does it mean? Some islands have symbols, but others don't...
Len: The ones that do also have names!
Emu: Hey, you're right! Here's Zombie Island, Mermaid Island and... Oh, this one's Android Island!
Rin: Wait, we met plushies from all these islands at that inn!
Rui: A thought crossed my mind while we were there...
Rui: These islands seem to be linked to the shows we've done in the past.
Luka: You may be right. But linked in what way...?
KAITO: What if...?
KAITO: What if this ship has already been to these places?
KAITO: It's like the journey you and the others have been on, Tsukasa. This ship seems to have traveled to all these other islands on its way to Star Island.
Tsukasa: This ship is like us...?
KAITO: I think so. More precisely, it's a physical manifestation of your present feelings, Tsukasa.
Tsukasa: My feelings...?
Tsukasa: (This ship traveled to all these islands in the hopes of reaching Star Island at the end.)
Tsukasa: (In that sense, we are one and the same. I have traveled far and done many things on my journey to stardom.)
Tsukasa: (And those feelings have manifested themselves in the form of this ship...?)
Tsukasa: (No, wait... I wasn't able to get here by myself.)
Tsukasa: (I met Emu and the others, and we began doing shows together. I came this far because of them.)
Tsukasa: (Which means...)
Tsukasa: That's it!
Emu: What's it?! Did you figure something out, Tsukasa?
Tsukasa: Yes, I think this place...
Tsukasa: It represents my desire to become a star while growing alongside my friends as we travel to different places.
Tsukasa: That may be what's behind all this.
KAITO: Yes, I'm inclined to agree.
Rui: I see.
Rui: Then, these symbols must represent our accomplishments...
Rui: Which means the ones that aren't are places we might be going to in the future.
Nene: Oh, now I see.
Emu: So, is there a way for us to get this ship to sail?!
Tsukasa: Huh?
Emu: We should all go together! To Star Island!
Tsukasa: Wh-What?! Is such a thing even possible...?
Emu: I'm not sure... But if that's where this ship wants to go, I think we should help it get there!
MEIKO: I agree! And we can go if we get it to sail!
Miku: I wanna go too! I need to see what Star Island looks like!
Nene: Yeah, but sailing a ship is easier said than done... Would we even be able to do that...?
Robo-Nene: Ship operation program available for installation.
Nene: No, Robo-Nene, I doubt you alone can get it to run. I'm pretty sure we're all gonna have to work together.
Emu: Then, what if we asked some of the plushies for help?
MEIKO: Great idea! It sounded like a lot of them in the harbor may know a thing or two about operating this vessel!
Len: Come to think of it, a lot of them said that they came here on boats and ships!
Rui: Hmm... Yes, asking them for help does seem like a good idea. Not only that, we appear to have everything we need for our journey, so we should be able to cast off whenever.
Tsukasa: I see. Naturally, I'll also be going!
Tsukasa: No matter the cost, I must see what Star Island looks like for myself!
Nene: Huh...?
Emu: What about you, Nene?! You're coming too, right?!
Nene: *Sigh* There's no way to stop you guys at this point, huh?
Nene: Fine, I'll go. I do also wanna see what Star Island looks like.
Tsukasa: Excellent! Then...
Tsukasa: Let's set sail to Star Island!
Tsukasa: Wh-Whyyy?!
Tsukasa: We keep getting pushed back every time we try to cast off...
Rui: The tide appears to be the problem. It may be why we keep getting sent back to port.
Rin: So, does that mean we can't go to Star Island...?
Miku: No, I'm sure we still can!
Emu: Huh?
Miku: I don't actually know, but I still think we can! Tsukasa, I believe that you and the others will make it to Star Island someday!
Miku: I have faith in you all!
Tsukasa: Miku...
KAITO: I agree with Miku.
KAITO: I believe that you'll get there someday, but that it's still too early for you.
Tsukasa: Still too early...?
KAITO: You don't see yourself as a star yet, do you, Tsukasa?
Tsukasa: I... Of course not.
KAITO: Then, as you and the others meet new people and continue to grow one step at a time...
KAITO: Your path to becoming a star may finally open up, and SEKAI may reflect that.
Tsukasa: Right. As I grow alongside the others...
Tsukasa: Alright! Let's do it!
Tsukasa: We'll grow as we sail the seas together on this long voyage... All while aboard the Pegasus Special Deluxe Wonder!
Nene: He already came up with a name for it...?
Rui: Hehe. I think it's good that he's so full of optimism.
Tsukasa: Emu! Nene! Rui!
Tsukasa: Our dreams may all be different. But we are all headed towards making them a reality.
Tsukasa: Let us keep pushing each other to become better as we strive to make them come true!
Emu, Nene & Rui: Yeah! Yes.
KAITO: Hehe. The four of you never change. You're always doing your best and working towards your dreams.
Miku: And we're gonna keep giving you guys all the support we can☆
Tsukasa: Ah, that would be greatly appreciated!
Tsukasa: So, let's do our usual thing to mark the occasion!
Emu: Okay! Ready, everyone?!
Tsukasa: We're going to keep pushing toward our dream!!!
Everyone: Let's do this, wonderhoy!!!
Len: Hehe. I can't wait to see how you guys' journey unfolds.
Miku: Me neither☆
Miku: Huh?
Miku: Hey, everyone! Look! There's something growing by the ship!
KAITO: Hm? That looks like... A plant? A sprout?
Rin: Oh, it's so adorably tiny☆
Luka: I don't know what kind of plant this is, but I have a feeling that it's going to grow big and strong...
MEIKO: Of course it's going to! After all, it's made from Tsukasa's feelings.
Len: Then, it's probably gonna end up being huge!
KAITO: I agree.
KAITO: So, let's keep a close eye on this little sprout while we watch Tsukasa and the others grow.
Miku: Yeah!
